"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-evie-richards-olympics-paris-2024-mountain-biking-b2583715.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Richards suffered a concussion in April but has fought back to make her second appearance at an Olympics  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  It took Evie Richards' mum to step in and tell her she needed to get off her bike.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\", \"score\": 0.9999999329950264, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evie Richards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evie_Richards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When theformer mountain bike world championcrashed during a World Cup race in Araxa, Brazil in April, she brushed herself off and declared there was \\\"no serious damage\\\", racing again the following day.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9982862909034097, \"rank\": 0.0015494891452329214, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in truth the 27-year-oldhad suffered a concussion- something she would struggle to admit even to herself.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think as soon as I crashed, I was like, 'no, I am fine',\\\" Richards told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That night, I put on makeup, put on a nice outfit and went down for dinner.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like, if I just look fine from the outside no one knows what's going on inside and I can just race.\\\"\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Commonwealth champion had suffered a concussion before while on Grant Ferguson's training camp in the build-up to the 2016Olympics, and knew many of the signs.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1134, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_of_Nations\", \"score\": 0.5729454799307531, \"rank\": 0.4912322586085223, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_of_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_of_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"score\": 0.9999999579677032, \"rank\": 4.20271864484058e-08, \"text\": \"Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\"}, {\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"score\": 0.9999869469101395, \"rank\": 1.262672009040613e-05, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Back then I did not really know it was a concussion but this time I knew,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I also knew the recovery time of concussion and I did not really want to accept it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was no longer possible after Richards had flown home and went for dinner with her family.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went for food with my parents and grandparents who I had not seen for a while and mum could see it in my eyes,\\\" Richards said.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was like, 'Evie, you are not right'.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not even have dinner with my family.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When your family say you are not right, you need to stop.\\\"\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Richards then spoke to British Cycling's medical team and began a proper programme of recovery, returning to racing at the British nationals in early June.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1868, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}, {\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9967467830895014, \"rank\": 0.00325875401649947, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the injury behind her, Richards was selected for her second Olympics at the end of June, but the last few months have been a huge learning process for her.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I am always the sort of person who will just 'crack on',\\\" Richards said.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I get that from my dad.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I wrote in my diary how bad I was (after the crash) and reading it back now, I am like, 'gosh, why did you even race the next day?'\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even when I raced the next day I did not feel right and did not for the next week.\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I just kept saying, 'oh, maybe it's the impact' and then, 'maybe it's jetlag, maybe I am just tired'.\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I was definitely at fault.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think when there is selection for the Olympics coming, when there is World Cups coming up, it's very hard to step away and take a break, which obviously would have been the best thing to do.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back, I know a lot more now.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it happens again, I will definitely handle it in a much different way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Richards will now look forward to her second Olympic appearance.\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She finishedseventh on debut in Tokyo, and weeks later stormed to the world title with victory in Val di Sole.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3035, \"end\": 3040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9802089950698322, \"rank\": 0.01901654535244601, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think anyone who knows me knows I got into sport because of the Olympics, it's all I have ever dreamt of,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think the excitement of being selected ever goes away.\\\"\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since returning to racing, Richards has had a podium finish with fifth place at the Crans-Montana World Cup, coming in sixth in Les Gets last weekend.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3386, \"end\": 3399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Crans-Montana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she will head to Parisstill with many unanswered questions.\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am super happy with the podium but I am taking it with a pinch of salt because I have not had the training or the run-up I need,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not really have any expectations currently on the Games.\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just love being a part of it.\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd love to medal but I can only get as fit as I can be in the time left.\\\"\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PA  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3976, \"entities\": []}]}"